<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>The <link linkend="_class_leap_1_1_image">Image</link> class represents a stereo image pair from the <link linkend="_namespace_leap">Leap</link> Motion device. </para>



<para>In addition to image data, the <link linkend="_class_leap_1_1_image">Image</link> object provides a distortion map for correcting lens distortion. <formalpara><title>Since: </title>

<para>2.1.0 </para>
</formalpara>
</para>
